Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Documentary papyrus
Description: Documentary papyrus. The heading (line 1-2) bears an address to a civil servant of high rank, who belonged to the "Diadochoi Kai pros têi suntaxei", but whose name is unknown. Next are eleven mutilated lines of which is legible only the verb "axiouu" (line 9), characteristic of the vocabulary of the petitions.
